* Streaming Tables\nfor Ingestion
** What They Are
***_ Delta table optimized for append
***_ Each record processed exactly once
***_ Ideal for append-only sources
** Sources
***_ Cloud storage (Auto Loader)
***_ Message queues
***_ JSON / CSV / Parquet files
** SQL Syntax
***_ CREATE OR REFRESH STREAMING TABLE
***_ STREAM read_files(...)
***_ Only new files processed
** Python Syntax
***_ @dp.table decorator
***_ spark.readStream
***_ Returns streaming DataFrame
@endmindmap
